  "lyrics": "I said, hey, what's that? God No, you got rude type men, is that how you wanna be? No, that's a rude boy type man, is that how you want to be? When you're rockin' with me, when you're rockin' all night Away, away Does it take more for you to understand? I'm more valuable than Getting fucked up every day, getting fucked up every night I said, hey, I know you got rude type men And I know it's fine Disaster floating on the edge of your mind Oh, no, you got that type men And I know you got bad type men I know you got that type men I know you got rude type men And it won't be the same I know you're wanting me to take my last name Your timing is insane I don't care anymore about your touch It don't matter I know you got rude type men And I know it's all in vain Fuck the way you are Taste me, erase me and fuck my fate I don't want it anymore Goodbye, erase",
